The Ninth Bolgia, in which are punished the
Schismatics, and
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
              "where is paid the fee
     By those who sowing discord win their burden";
..TEXT:
a burden difficult to describe even with untrammelled
words, or in plain prose, free from the fetters of rhyme.
